org.opendaylight.controller.sal.implementation.internal

Class ReadService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.implementation.internal.ReadService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandProvider, IPluginOutReadService, IReadService

    public class ReadService
extends java.lang.Object
implements IReadService, CommandProvider, IPluginOutReadService
    The SAL Read Service. Dispatches read requests to the proper SDN protocol plugin, and notifies any listeners on updates from any plugin readers
